your your first year that one semester before you went into the Navy. Quite a

14:35.740 --> 14:40.980
good luck in young man. Wow. And then the next photo is a little later when you

14:40.980 --> 14:47.380
were in a Navy photograph so this was taken just a few years later. Yes. Right.

